## Notes For Next Iteration

- Voice search: H5 uses browser MediaRecorder + backend ASR; miniprogram uses WechatSI plugin (no backend ASR needed); Flutter uses record plugin + backend ASR. ASR config managed via admin panel (搜索管理 → 语音配置).
- Merchant identities are granted by admin only; new self-registered accounts still default to normal users.
- Old user and merchant accounts require admin-side manual merge before official cutover.
- If remote DB schema lags behind models, check startup schema synchronization and the new merchant-related tables first.
- SMS config can be managed from admin panel (系统管理 → 短信管理). Supports dual provider (Tencent Cloud + Alibaba Cloud), only one active at a time. DB config takes priority over env vars.
- To enable real SMS sending: configure via admin panel (dual provider supported) or set `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_ID` and `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_KEY` environment variables.
- WeChat push config: 系统管理 → 微信推送管理. Email notify config: 系统管理 → 邮件通知管理 (with logs and test send).
- The old `POST /api/admin/settings/push` endpoint is deprecated (returns 410 Gone). Use the new independent module APIs instead.
- OCR multi-provider: Configure via admin panel (AI管理 → OCR识别配置). Supports Baidu/Tencent/Aliyun with smart failover. At least 2 providers recommended for failover.
- OCR AI post-processing: Scene templates drive AI structured output with embedded prompt_content. Presets: 体检报告识别, 拍照识药. Custom scenes can be added.
- OCR global settings: Configure via admin panel (AI管理 → OCR全局设置). Scene templates and upload limits are managed here. Scene templates contain scene_name + prompt_content only (no ocr_provider/ai_model_id).
- OCR prompt management: Prompts are now embedded directly in scene templates (OcrSceneTemplate.prompt_content), no longer stored in AiPromptConfig table.
- OCR detail tables: `checkup_report_details` and `drug_identify_details` store business-specific fields extracted from AI results. Admin pages: AI管理 → 体检报告解读明细 / 拍照识药记录明细.
- Checkup report (2026-04-08): enhanced analyze + compare APIs; H5 `/checkup/compare`, miniprogram `checkup-compare`, Flutter `/report-compare`; `health_score` on `CheckupReport`.
- Home dynamic config (2026-04-08): `home_menu_items` and `home_banners` tables; 8 system_config keys for search/grid/font settings; admin CRUD APIs + user public APIs; admin-web 3 new pages under "首页配置"; all three client ends (H5/miniprogram/Flutter) now fetch banners/menus/config from API instead of hardcoded data; font size 3-level switching with local persistence.
- Unified search (2026-04-08): H5-only, 7 new DB tables (SearchHistory, SearchHotWord, SearchRecommendWord, SearchBlockWord, SearchLog, AsrConfig, DrugSearchKeyword); H5 `/search` and `/search/result` pages; admin "搜索管理" menu with 4 sub-pages (推荐搜索词, 搜索统计, 屏蔽词管理, 语音配置). Block words checked server-side before search. ASR SecretKey encrypted. Default drug keywords: 拍照识药, 识药, 药品识别, 拍药, 认药.
- Emoji icon picker expansion (2026-04-09): Pure frontend change in `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/home-menus/page.tsx`. `EMOJI_CATEGORIES` expanded from 7 to 14 categories (added: 科技数码, 人物表情, 交通工具, 建筑地标, 天气时间, 办公学习, 金融商务). `EMOJI_LABEL_MAP` expanded from 260+ to 500+ entries for richer Chinese search. Existing categories (运动健身, 食物饮料, 自然植物, 动物) also received supplemental Emoji entries. Category tab bar restyled with smaller padding/font for 14-category layout with `flexWrap: 'wrap'`. No backend/DB changes.
